quran[7]{c,v,t,f}:
  25,1,"Most blessed is He Who sent down this Criterion on His servant, to be a warner to all mankind;"{1}{2}{3}{4},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3,footnotes:4:4
  25,2,"He to Whom belongs the kingdom of the heavens and the earth; Who has taken to Himself no son nor has He taken any partner in His kingdom; Who created everything and then determined its destiny."{1}{2}{3}{4},footnotes:1:1,footnotes:2:2,footnotes:3:3,footnotes:4:4